aims-os-security (2.0) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Carved out of aims-os-math to align with the AIMS
    Coop Computer Security filière. Depends on aims-os-math so
    installing it on a vanilla Debian Trixie pulls the full SciPy / R /
    LaTeX baseline.
    Crypto primitives: python3-cryptography, python3-pycryptodome
    (Qiskit stays install-on-demand via pipx since Debian's package
    lags upstream).
    Ethical Hacking / Network Security: nmap, wireshark, tcpdump,
    john, hashcat, aircrack-ng, python3-scapy.
    Forensics: sleuthkit, foremost, binwalk.

